    Delete
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Delete</TypeRef> method destroys the null logger object.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Objects returned through <TypeRef>ILogger::unique_ptr</TypeRef> are normally destroyed by the smart pointer deleter rather than by calling this method directly.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void Delete() override;]]></Code>
  </Section>
